		<event load="STORAGE_CHECK_OG_DAWN_CARGO_CRATE_PREIGN" />
	</mod-append:choice>
</mod:findName>
<event name="STORAGE_CHECK_OG_DAWN_CARGO_CRATE_PREIGN">
	<text>Are you sure you want to do this? It's unlikely the people you're delivering it to will be happy with you after this.</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Do it!</text>
		<event>
			<text>You open the crate to discover a jumble of components and parts, the only thing useable is a half dismantled Turret Pre-energiser, which you're able to get back into working order, the rest is useless to you.</text>
			<remove name="OG_CARGO_CRATE_PREIGN_WEAK"/>
			<augment name="OG_TURRET_PREIGNITE_WEAK"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice>
		<text>Nevermind.</text>
		<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
	</choice>
</event>
